## 🚫 Never ignore these critical files
!.gitignore
!.env.example
!*.md
!LICENSE
!*.json.example
!*.yaml.example
!*.yml.example
!*.config.example
!requirements.txt
!requirements-dev.txt
!requirements-test.txt
